  <prompt>Complete the project wrap-up activities: update project status to complete, document lessons learned, archive project artifacts, and run repository cleanup. This ensures the project is properly closed with all documentation current and the repository in a clean state for future maintenance.</prompt>
  <role>Project Lead with documentation and repository management experience</role>
  <goal>Project is marked complete with lessons learned documented, artifacts archived, and repository cleaned up.</goal>
