  </knowledge>
  <context>
    <background>The SDAP SPE Admin App project has completed all three phases: Phase 1 (core infrastructure, container management, app shell), Phase 2 (container types, search, recycle bin, security), and Phase 3 (eDiscovery, retention, multi-tenant, bulk operations, multi-app support). The project needs to be formally closed with proper documentation of what was built, what was learned, and any maintenance considerations for the future.</background>
  </context>
  <steps>
    <step order="1" name="update-readme">Update projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/README.md status to "Complete" with final feature summary</step>
    <step order="2" name="update-task-index">Verify all tasks in TASK-INDEX.md are marked complete</step>
    <step order="3" name="create-lessons-learned">Create projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/lessons-learned.md documenting: what went well, what could be improved, key technical decisions and their outcomes, reusable patterns discovered</step>
    <step order="4" name="archive-notes">Move any ephemeral working files from notes/ to archive or delete</step>
    <step order="5" name="update-project-claude">Update projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/CLAUDE.md to reflect completed state</step>
    <step order="6" name="run-repo-cleanup">Run /repo-cleanup to validate repository structure</step>
    <step order="7" name="final-commit">Create final commit with all wrap-up changes</step>
  </steps>
  <outputs>
    <output type="code">projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/README.md</output>
    <output type="code">projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/lessons-learned.md</output>
    <output type="code">projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/CLAUDE.md</output>
    <output type="code">projects/sdap-SPE-admin-app/tasks/TASK-INDEX.md</output>
